<p></p>



<p>Fireflies are some of nature&#8217;s most beautiful and mysterious creations and it&#8217;s unfortunate that we are seeing less and less of them where we live. Thank you for visiting this site and be sure to read about our section about <a href="https://www.firefly.org/how-you-can-help.html">how your can help firelies return</a> in your area and <a href="https://www.firefly.org/certify">how to certify your habitat</a> for fireflies.</p>
